headline: Cruise demand shows mixed signals as bookings hold up into 2026
summary: Investing.com -- Cruise demand ended the summer on a mixed note, with signs of resilience in bookings for 2026 but some discounting creeping into the limited remaining 2025 inventory, according to Morgan Stanley.

headline: THE WAIT IS OVER - CELEBRITY CRUISES INTRODUCES THE MOST INNOVATIVE SHIPS ON THE RIVER
summary: The future of river cruising has arrived. Celebrity Cruises is bringing transformative ships with open decks, spacious staterooms, unmatched dining and its signature elevated hospitality to the Rhine and Danube rivers – offering guests the chance to river vacation The Celebrity Way. Priority Booking Access is now open for 2027 sailings on the groundbreaking Celebrity Compass and Celebrity Seeker.
